{"title":"石头城","authors":["黄东成"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":9,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"石头城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄东成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古都的编年史，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈列在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宫廷式建筑的博物院，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毁坏了城墙的厚线装书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是六朝十代的档案。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一个王朝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都留下御道街，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一代代风流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被推出午门问斩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石头城的石头历尽灾劫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何须再去寻城墙上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史的“鬼脸”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虎踞龙盘的风水宝地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今已是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一城繁华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一城鲜妍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"载入古城新的一页，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中山陵、雨花台、梅园"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凸现在字里行间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浓荫夹道的法国梧桐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一行行绿色装订线。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快车道慢车道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞驰着速度，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现代流行色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将斑马线撩乱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿红蝙蝠衫的少女"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"含着紫雪糕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"观赏御道街"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"温习往事千年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千年的“六朝旧事随流水”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时代从三十七层大厦的璇宫鸟瞰："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胭脂井圈石似尘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈后主残梦如烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朱洪武留下一带城墙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曹雪芹文章不胫而传，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那小小的大总统府，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依傍在太平天国的沉舟侧畔……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦，兴亡中变幻的古城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似一幅耐人寻味的油画。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秦淮河沉淀了多少"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桨橹欸乃的记忆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石头城的大脑皮层上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刻就了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一部史诗一排和弦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新街口用信息爆炸感光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摄下一卷卷彩色录像片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"底版上有古都的痕迹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"显影的是新城的变迁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个弧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个伟大的过渡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个少女"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个妩媚的笑靥。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":15,"page_end":15}